snippet.title: AYE
snippet.description:
Welcome! AYE (alex yates engineering) is a newly formed company, that specialises in the design, prototyping, and manufacture of small parts, using a range of cnc machining and fabrication processes. We are located in the South Hams area of Devon, in the United Kingdom.

Please visit our website www.aye.company for more information.
